title: Canadian Pacific (1949 Western) Randolph Scott | A Land to Conquer... A Love to Win!

sources.title: Canadian Pacific (1949 Western) Randolph Scott | A Land to Conquer... A Love to Win!
sources.description:
Rugged surveyor Tom Andrews (Randolph Scott) battles fur trader Dirk Rourke (Victor Jory) to save the railroad, while caught in a love triangle between fiery Cecille (Nancy Olson) and pacifist doctor Edith (Jane Wyatt). Explosions, romance, and mountain vistas collide in this classic Western adventure

Original title: Canadian Pacific (1949)

Director: Edwin L. Marin
Writers: Jack DeWitt, Kenneth Gamet

Main Actors: 
Randolph Scott - Tom Andrews
Jane Wyatt - Dr. Edith Cabot
J. Carrol Naish - Dynamite Dawson
Victor Jory - Dirk Rourke
Nancy Olson - Cecille Gautier
Robert Barrat - Cornelius Van Horne
Walter Sande - Mike Brannigan
Don Haggerty - Cagle
John Parrish - Mr. Gautier
Mary Kent - Mrs. Gautier

Release date: April 29, 1949
Filming locations: Banff National Park and Morley, Alberta, Canada.
